    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>bacon lardons </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to brown</p>",
